<title>HUNGARY: CSFB calls option for 120,420 Zalakeramia shares.</title>
<headline>CSFB calls option for 120,420 Zalakeramia shares.</headline>
<dateline>BUDAPEST 1997-06-09</dateline>
<text>
<p>Credit Suisse First Boston (Europe) Ltd (CSFB) called an over-allotment option for buying 120,420 shares of Hungarian tile maker Zalakeramia said on Monday in the Budapest Stock Exchange's (BSE) official gazette.</p>
<p>Zalakeramia placed privately 1,042,000 new shares in May, and CSFB had an overallotment option for buying 156,420 shares altogether, according to earlier press reports.</p>
<p>Zalakeramia closed at 7,745 forints on the BSE on Friday.</p>
<p>-- Budapest newsroom (36 1) 327 4040.</p>
